Brussels has narrowed its long-running antitrust probe against Apple, focus=
ing on the way the tech giant restricts apps such as Spotify from telling u=
sers about alternative subscription options. The European Commission on Tue=
sday said it was now investigating how apps were allegedly prevented from t=
elling iPhone and iPad users of cheaper ways to access music subscriptions =
outside of the App Store. The narrowing of the probe means the commission h=
as abandoned a separate charge that accused Apple of forcing developers to =
use its own in-app payment system.

From the European Commission=E2=80=99s press release ( https://ec.europa.eu=
